@AA_HostAddress = https://localhost:5001

### Health Check - Liveness
GET {{AA_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check - Readiness
GET {{AA_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

### Register New User
POST {{AA_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123",
  "fullName": "John Doe"
}

###

### Login
POST {{AA_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

###
